---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Biohacking Coach Lakeway TX | EmpowerX3 Body Mind Spirit"
  description="EmpowerX3 is Lakeway's biohacking wellness center. 90-day transformation coaching, ExoPod 10-in-1 recovery therapy, and Wolfpack group hikes. Gary Brandt, biohacking & medical weight loss coach."
>

  <!-- ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-900 via-brand-800 to-brand-700 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-brand-300 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          Lakeway, TX · Biohacking · Medical Weight Loss · Life Coaching
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
          A Biohacking Coach Who Lets Your Body Lead Your Healing
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-100 leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-2xl">
          Something's off with life. You're wildly successful in one or two areas, but something isn't clicking.
          Maybe it's your health, your career and family, or even your faith. You've tried keto, bought the supplements,
          hired the coaches and therapists. You know what you want to change. And you're still stuck.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-accent-300 font-semibold mb-8">
          Guess what: you're not failing. You're just using the wrong tool combination.
          Give me 90 days and people will be asking you what the secret is — just like they did with me.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-accent-500 text-white font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-accent-600 transition-colors"
          >
            Book a Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="/tools"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-brand-400 text-brand-100 font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-brand-700 transition-colors"
          >
            Explore the ExoPod
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Three Pillars ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        {[
          { icon: '💪', label: 'Body', desc: 'Discover the physical tools that restore your energy, reduce pain, and reset your biology.' },
          { icon: '🧠', label: 'Mind', desc: 'Build the mindset behind your power. Connect daily action to your deepest vision.' },
          { icon: '✨', label: 'Spirit', desc: 'Build unshakeable faith in yourself as you transform — from the inside out.' },
        ].map(({ icon, label, desc }) => (
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <span class="text-4xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">{icon}</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">{label}</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Gary's Story ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">About Gary Brandt</p>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Biohacking Life Coach · Medical Weight Loss Coach · Pain & Recovery Center Owner
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            After a car accident left me permanently disabled, doctors told me I'd never get my life back.
            I tried fixing my body alone. Then my mind. Then my spirit. Nothing worked until I worked on
            all three at the same time.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            That's when things clicked into place and I saw measurable success in every aspect of my
            life — not just one.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Everything I teach is something I've physically done, experienced, and personally used.
            No theory. No borrowed expertise. Just a complete system that works because it's complete.
            You have more control than you think. You just need all three legs of the stool.
          </p>
          <a href="/solutions" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-800 transition-colors">
            See the 90-Day Program &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-100">
          <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-lg italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "I've lived every failure you've lived. I've done every diet, taken every supplement,
            believed every promise that didn't deliver. I don't teach theory — I teach what I've personally
            used to overcome a permanently disabling injury and decades of trauma."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="font-semibold text-brand-700">— Gary Brandt, Founder of EmpowerX3</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Pain Points ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">
          Traditional Treatments Have Left You With More Questions Than Answers
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mb-10">Does your day look like this?</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          {[
            'Energy crashes that ruin your afternoons and steal your joy',
            'Pain that makes simple movement feel like punishment',
            'A brain that knows exactly what to do but a body that won\'t cooperate',
            'The quiet shame of being brilliant at everything except the one thing that keeps you alive',
            'Watching your friends struggle and knowing you\'re on the same path',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-red-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✗</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-center text-lg font-semibold text-brand-700">
          The truth is that <em>you</em> aren't failing. Your current plan is failing <em>you</em>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── ExoPod Intro ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-10 text-center text-white">
          <span class="text-7xl block mb-4" aria-hidden="true">🛸</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl mb-2">The ExoPod</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Lakeway's first all-in-one wellness pod</p>
          <p class="text-accent-400 font-bold text-lg mt-4">10 Therapies. One Session. Zero Effort.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">No Pills. No Needles. No Downtime.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Reset Your Biology in 30 Minutes
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Introducing EmpowerX3's signature cellular recovery experience: the ExoPod.
            This isn't just another wellness device — it's a clinical-grade biohacking tool that delivers
            10 advanced therapies in one 30-minute session.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Inflammation, slow recovery, and premature aging aren't character flaws. They're cellular problems.
            And cellular problems require cellular solutions. The ExoPod is your reset button.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/tools"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-brand-700 transition-colors"
          >
            See All 10 Therapies &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── CTA Banner ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="bg-brand-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">
        Ready to Work on All Three at the Same Time?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-brand-200 text-lg mb-3">
        Visit us at Lohman's Crossing in Lakeway, TX — or book a discovery call to start remotely.
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm mb-8">2300 Lohmans Spur #116 · Lakeway, TX 78734</p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-accent-500 text-white font-bold text-lg hover:bg-accent-600 transition-colors"
      >
        Book My Free Discovery Call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
